258
00:23:10,520 --> 00:23:11,680
Oke.

259
00:23:26,520 --> 00:23:27,880
Aku akan mengambilnya.

260
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:32,520
Terima kasih, P'Dindin.

261
00:23:32,760 --> 00:23:34,680
Tentu saja. Aku berangkat kalau begitu.

262
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:37,360
Sampai besok. Sampai jumpa.

263
00:23:37,360 --> 00:23:38,480
Sampai jumpa.

264
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:43,640
- Aku pergi.
- Lihat ya.

265
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:46,080
